      "content": "i know a helpline can talk to me but they don't get it. they're just gonna say \"it gets better\" or something like that. but it doesn't feel like it's gonna get better. everything i built, everything i was, it's all just gone. it feels like there's no point in trying to fix something that's already completely broken. i just feel so tired of the struggle.",
