      "content": "it’s not just \"grief\" though. it’s like... the version of me that existed with them is dead. and i'm just this ghost left behind. i look in the mirror and i don't even recognize the person staring back. it feels like i'm just waiting for something to happen, but nothing ever does. i'm just stuck in this loop of hurting. sometimes i just wish i could opt out of the loop entirely. i just want the noise to stop.",
